WEBVTT

01:15.874 --> 01:19.078
got your bibles and I hope that you do open up to Matthew chapter 5.

01:19.158 --> 01:24.165
Matthew chapter 5 is where we're going to be this morning as we're starting a new series called High Impact.

01:24.386 --> 01:38.685
